# Fastlane plugins.
#
# This file is read by the Gemfile so `bundle install` picks up every
# plugin alongside Fastlane itself. Keep plugins minimal -- every extra
# gem extends CI install time.
#
# IMPORTANT: Fastlane's Pluginfile is for gems named `fastlane-plugin-*`
# ONLY. Fastlane auto-requires those at startup so their actions
# self-register. Listing a non-plugin gem (e.g. `xcov`, `cocoapods`)
# here makes fastlane warn "plugins couldn't be loaded" at startup --
# put those in `Gemfile` instead. `xcov` lives in Gemfile alongside
# fastlane + cocoapods; the `xcov` Fastfile action is auto-discovered
# once the gem is bundle-loaded.

# Versioning helper -- bumps Info.plist / xcconfig version + build numbers
# consistently. Built-in but pinning the gem ensures CI uses the same.
